<article>
  <div class="community-cards">
    <div class="headline-container">
      <%= link_to connecting_path do %>
      <h2 class="headline" >Connecting</h2>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    Connect to UO Second age! Download the client, run Razor and start your journey!
    <%= link_to 'Full story', connecting_path, class:"small" %>
  </div>

  <div class="community-cards">
    <div class="headline-container">
      <%= link_to beginning_path do %>
      <h2 class="headline condensed">Beginning Britannia</h2>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    The world of Britannia is vast and filled with excitement and danger, but before you begin your adventure, we recommend you explore these quick tips on getting started!
    <%= link_to 'Full story', bnn_path, class:"small" %>
  </div>

  <div class="community-cards">
    <div class="headline-container">
      <%= link_to events_path do %>
      <h2 class="headline condensed">Britannian Professions</h2>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    From Archers to Bards to Carpenters, we've gathered a few tips on choosing the right skills to complement your newfound profession in Britannia.
    <%= link_to 'Full story', events_path, class:"small" %>
  </div>

  <div class="community-cards">
    <div class="headline-container">
      <%= link_to rules_path do %>
      <h2 class="headline condensed">Britannian Etiquette</h2>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    Over 23,000 player run organizations, or guilds, permeate the landscape of UO. Each guild, ranging in size from just a few members to over 200 in the largest, conducts meetings and plans adventures. Our page reflect rankings and warfare status' and are growing in features all the time.
    <%= link_to 'Full story', rules_path, class:"small" %>
  </div>

  <div class="community-cards">
    <div class="headline-container">
      <%= link_to events_path do %>
      <h2 class="headline condensed">Meet the Community</h2>
      <% end %>
    </div>
