    <%= link_to 'Full story', events_path, class:"small" %>
  </div>

  <div class="community-cards">
    <div class="headline-container">
      <%= link_to events_path do %>
      <h2 class="headline">Meet the Staff</h2>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    Designed to support both the newest visitor and the veteran player, the assistance programs of Ultima Online promote players helping players. You'll find details on all of our Customer Support programs and how they can help you.
    <%= link_to 'Full story', events_path, class:"small" %>
  </div>


  </article>
